Copyright 2026 stslam

This repository contains build tooling, source patches, and pre-built
binaries for using libmdbx with Embarcadero RAD Studio / C++ Builder
(bcc32c / bcc64x, tested with RAD Studio 13.1).

It does NOT contain a copy of the libmdbx source tree. The patches/
directory contains unified diffs meant to be applied on top of:

    https://github.com/stslam/libmdbx_embarcadero (branch: work_on)

which is itself a fork tracking:

    libmdbx (aka MDBX) — an extremely fast, compact, powerful, embeddable,
    transactional key-value storage engine.
    Copyright 2015-2026 Леонид Юрьев (Leonid Yuriev) <leo@yuriev.ru>
    SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0
    Origin / primary source: https://sourcecraft.dev/dqdkfa/libmdbx
    Documentation: https://libmdbx.dqdkfa.ru

Pre-built binaries under bin/ are compiled from the above source plus
the patches in patches/, using the scripts in build/. They are provided
as a convenience for Embarcadero users and carry the same Apache-2.0
license as libmdbx itself. See LICENSE for the full license text.

This is an unofficial, community-maintained build; it is not affiliated
with, endorsed by, or supported by the libmdbx maintainer.
